{"type":"message","id":"e0d7da71","parentId":"04db3ed6","timestamp":"2026-05-07T22:16:13.955Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e5uVgGSUGIXpfgMytmxPuhxX|fc_089f5c82f7390fab0169fd0f2387248191901fceaf8bab17e8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.6 (c97b9f7) — The only open-source project where the mascot could eat the competition.\n\nUsage: openclaw mcp [options] [command]\n\nManage OpenClaw MCP config and channel bridge\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  list        List configured MCP servers\n  serve       Expose OpenClaw channels over MCP stdio\n  set         Set one configured MCP server from a JSON object\n  show        Show one configured MCP server or the full MCP config\n  unset       Remove one configured MCP server\n\n--- current config path ---\n~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\n--- mcp config get ---\n{\n  \"servers\": {\n    \"socraticode\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"-y\",\n        \"socraticode\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"puppeteer\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"-y\",\n        \"@kirkdeam/puppeteer-mcp-server\"\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n--- tools mcp config get ---\nConfig path not found: tools.mcp\n\n--- validate ---\nConfig valid: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8060,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.6 (c97b9f7) — The only open-source project where the mascot could eat the competition.\n\nUsage: openclaw mcp [options] [command]\n\nManage OpenClaw MCP config and channel bridge\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  list        List configured MCP servers\n  serve       Expose OpenClaw channels over MCP stdio\n  set         Set one configured MCP server from a JSON object\n  show        Show one configured MCP server or the full MCP config\n  unset       Remove one configured MCP server\n\n--- current config path ---\n~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\n--- mcp config get ---\n{\n  \"servers\": {\n    \"socraticode\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"-y\",\n        \"socraticode\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"puppeteer\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"-y\",\n        \"@kirkdeam/puppeteer-mcp-server\"\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n--- tools mcp config get ---\nConfig path not found: tools.mcp\n\n--- validate ---\nConfig valid: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778192173955}}
