y_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering MCP configuration**\\n\\nI need to figure out if I should add sequential or ollama, and whether to include filesystem or terminal components. The user asked about the three main MCP aspects, including filesystem and terminal. Since OpenClaw already has exec, read, and write functionalities, I might need to look into MCP configuration options. I should check what `openclaw mcp set --help` provides to guide my next steps.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"🧑🏼‍💻 [เรียกใช้เครื่องมือ: exec]","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_089f5c82f7390fab0169fd0f329be88191b3cd8990cb1fe167\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0mzFiTDfv9gbyfgGtZasS6CM|fc_089f5c82f7390fab0169fd0f32a7a08191a4ec33f0102d6908","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw mcp set --help && printf '\\n--- list ---\\n' && openclaw mcp list","workdir":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.5","usage":{"input":607,"output":142,"cacheRead":35840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36589,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778192174016,"responseId":"resp_089f5c82f7390fab0169fd0f2eb22081918bfb360ebe5caeca"}}
