{"type":"message","id":"1f289415","parentId":"9fd1a9ee","timestamp":"2026-05-07T22:16:41.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering package installation**\n\nI need to add some configuration and decide if I want to use npx to install packages, since the user requested that. We'll install locally in the `/.openclaw/mcp-node` directory instead of globally. I need to run `npm init` and install both the `seq` and `filesystem` along with `ollama-mcp-server`. OpenClaw has built-in exec tools, so I wonder if we actually need any other terminal packages. I might also check for terminal package searches in npm.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_089f5c82f7390fab0169fd0f43249c81918d301c31887ba505\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_Q9JtmfxBvAAFcwSWhNcGVq2lWaO0oDDCnpQaL0m2hvk8TqDJlCuS6qANtXj_zPi3RH-OFE2C-zWMxgjulO86zBX890XWTB3APQAQR_BbZC87cxhrh_wn7_uMlDkmlg_lK1cGJSwT9MzlIcX1ardL-x9mh5rFXpu3sKL5ghWIwN4t0j9O9caCuCdGT-Yl8Pzf8numtZTy-OyX5eU2QmpdypiN0Gr5Jp43lUOqvNerTeNuHt_SL6z1nYOxB-NNCnazilIOOB6vzqlCg6Afpo8uqxp5jBEVzQisjfDpfU_XWhJLQxfT-P_rT8Us_-Zou9PVF88owiHeFP4Mf8oXM040J8jWdqOVecDOcNIxKj0HtoHXYkHmrMk0IpWkN2izQDPTIXBT0x2LHt61_wS01sxEuO1GtAVWqPhUpmt72vlBGVzgVFeMXXC-sDZGLFM7Ru9MXEA19MK_cibS8LMf5c18efcFqv2fNxObfEqYJhJ4n4_goOsYFl2EYzxwPETjNw9Uhk3mOjt4y_P25IKs7bjciuQu7psiptEW_Ym8B0YHe2OL1I_ZkoEPWWdQqnvSRFsafyzy72JjOU-WXjLLW8aqMvcaVW4yXt2BX2le_4rxTdQFcLTdLRuU_MFPEpNgtyGxl-PS677mV6Grzgob3NiOfUr1cOl8pzRQ-LEr41WY_KlXANUv-Vbv2v4V4KpMYJxXQhXaqcLcjJes9cH5XtF4dlVB3Ymdp8RnCqgkiDTRqGsVacJk1gzL8vH_g4eLGT_8oWAloxICg0VgyV6mJWWlByKK_p-IHHfLfKc-oLOL3jMHt-ivyHm9cinqyYk89wqWVrTOIpQyyLnWxd3KsZ5PncSiZk03hj80ZStoK6hPL7DngZVVymqn3xpx7AgEvhCCf_NuPhUnnlo5PH_jhTrJ1LhLE5dyjFH4l13LV21bVSDxrFfIU32RLli3-mQ7ITPt4ERyivonFx_FEzEqRonCFMoX-KT_RyIi9Jh1eVqlpxlSRtIPT9hIUA-sKc4IuTvafs1CqzBeaCtVCOOdxC3or94FsKfc9Ca5uz_KS72m0q6g1F09ngtK5pvkg-Ee8NECoMtLtDYOvJWMQjP9aH5BPhov_NCcyxk-VDKz8rTx_qax5jbC0UBhN2O-UZR90i2j7WZSSKykt-gCV9tQJpvu4TG-zdMjqf0nYUVD1iknTlVd9