{"type":"message","id":"7b2de626","parentId":"af604519","timestamp":"2026-05-07T22:21:39.454Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Troubleshooting gateway service**\n\nI’m trying to figure out why the gateway service is deactivating. Connectivity seems fine, but the service status shows it's stopped, which is concerning. Maybe I need to restart it from the command line? It could be problematic due to an active session. I might consider using systemctl, but I see that OpenClaw CLI has a command for restarting the gateway. I’ll also want to check the status later to ensure it’s stable.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_089f5c82f7390fab0169fd10718f3881918c3682cc6c5cf840\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_RB0Qhb-gL4fxCm_quI0ilMsNQEcnYnyPTV81zXlP44FpMPfQdUe3bzXubw0SUQct7XyruNtnm22ddzweDQ1LpVBRs4AtNU8PhmNeJ5Jck7h7xGZJf_PjTdI0pOLEbH8Ciikw7VwkLR_pd8lqVYsWicsyb8ReMrUOgCc02Lds3rWB-fqq1A60Loln8jFqqOTrNWDNIYvFEqGN-7Sieb_6TFUeTTxr9Ejgs6E1YsUx_3KoKvLesRJrskRv8Rbffw5kA3YezsS8gV3qTZ-iMfAlJsOkanBV1IvJElppqlhLMKlX5Qe3QCrVCn6EDfo7EWo53VHG8mXl_4M9xC1SHpu9H1ix1QLecN5xX5249Ts8f4E7lPrVDkbNubaTTt3cUyoWtz6Qhl0uv8GKGps_t5ZBH8rAuHpm1mHyt0C78NQB0l32yeWJG9-BrQs5yjerr6lQIgWJLOlmep5RPw7NbJ7p71-juYj2LJcC36ii7jpyLTUzpvrMoovDLUsLfhKmc1_l2i0kP1KBOYhYMEKjgvNBByi2pjffsR9vfD5Zk4rkdtWx66cmGtdJXUCK0qTHNXU9ekpFgE70_u3si4OPFxgmJPu-IcHUh3ABhsoEqxUlOwNWqlyoO22T_QPNUsKLzc7yDzqz-IRYfzhFQi3NqVchKsZGyPna5dseF12_sNwF-8w52rCQli6cXoqp7rVvszt317i1COZ1_bmKDDUUlNCOuVCFA8hBnGyKfSgzQozG1RcjXH9MqoGJ0fwnVaPgh4XGT1syWnlRWowtW87HhhYfzPwiqLhJnmzm6LE1bmiGzr-ExLeAk6I73spay5XIBLNFse0zsdc4iBhnXuVYOtSN_y7iS4qQN1Q34L4XdPCKni5TV4JrgmRH7VEku3V0MfGxmt2zsfJ97mVQwo6vzVe-bm6DlAhCpRm9RJu1AWNaWqRyEMybXufad7qIH8gKKMc_9o4yv6BJqdWkUx-4w23sN0xTiFqXEwvCtgDZK11ZlHljKg_kJtCTgaOXZPjf5V0v1G2E8yR4PeIn9fl1PvkiAnrAY77L61QUnYCAbxrhl70BK9QC4kyIWNehWbi_qIxa1nNDLQp9Dqp4zh_4tcSeajMCO1q4YKMYen-2aNdzJpb0pYIkCWpUxdAbv9p84SWMXtGYwzi5PZ08q-o3spGGYWO6a3gh5pOyWPvOxSl3qeZsw4yjXfOfSO0_BD0hP_yFVqR82FT4N6I