{"type":"message","id":"6be835f7","parentId":"4cb53380","timestamp":"2026-05-07T23:50:03.830Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Let me verify the final result.","thinkingSignature":"2dfb6c4a09d5766d1d3eb043d2e9ee0d407b5d803d07719ee68ec16cca539161"},{"type":"text","text":"🧑🏼‍💻 แก้เรียบร้อยครับเจ้านาย อัปเดต Dynamic Status Logic แล้ว\n\nตั้งแต่นี้ต่อไป:\n1. **เริ่มงาน** → ส่งข้อความสถานะ 1 ข้อความ\n2. **ระหว่างทำ** → แก้ไขข้อความเดิม (Edit Message) เมื่อสลับโมเดล\n3. **จบงาน** → ลบข้อความสถานะ แล้วส่งคำตอบสุดท้าย\n\nรูปแบบ: `🧠 [สมองหลัก]: ...`, `🛠️ [Hermes (Local)]: ...`, `🖋️ [MiniMax]: ...`\n\nถ้าระบบไม่รองรับ Edit Message จะใช้วิธี Unsend ตามกฎเดิมครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":153005,"output":315,"cacheRead":32667,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":185987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778197793689,"responseId":"064c58245f60f31fafb1af0932915c30"}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"4c65fc1a","parentId":"6be835f7","timestamp":"2026-05-07T23:50:44.488Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Set up 3 MCP servers in OpenClaw (sequential-thinking, filesystem, ollama) for cost-saving \"Triple-Agent\" routing\n2. Configure Ollama with `hermes3:8b` as local worker model (RTX 4060 Ti)\n3. Establish clean output rules so Telegram chat stays uncluttered while showing task progress\n4. Ongoing memory/instruction management in OpenClaw workspace\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Work ONLY in OpenClaw side — do NOT touch Hermes/Mes_bot config/service without explicit permission\n- Hermes Permission Skill blocks any Hermes-related actions without user approval\n- Always use SocratiCode before reading/editing code files\n- Thai language only\n- Silent tool usage — no `[เรียกใช้เครื่องมือ: ...]` spam in Telegram\n- Log/status messages should be brief emoji-based and auto-deleted when possible\n- Final messages should show only the result the user actually needs\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Installed `@modelcontextprotocol/server-sequential-thinking`, `@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem`, `ollama-mcp-server` locally in `~/.openclaw/mcp-node` (npm install complete, 2 high-severity audit warnings noted but not acted on)\n- [x] Configured 3 MCP servers in OpenClaw: `sequential-thinking`, `filesystem` (with paths `/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace`, `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Downloads`, `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Pictures`), `ollama` (OLLAMA_HOST=http://127.0.0.1:11434)\n- [x] Pulled Ollama models: `hermes3:8b` (4.7GB, Q4_0 — primary worker), `qwen2.5:3b`, `moondream`, `nomic-embed-text` (kept for SocratiCode embeddings)\n- [x] Deleted `llama3.1:8b` and `phi3.5:latest` per user order\n- [x] Tested `ollama run hermmes3:8b` — responds \"READY\"\n- [x] Updated MEMORY.md with **Flexible Brain Protocol** (replacing \"Triple-Agent\"): current model = Architect, MiniMax = Content Creator, Hermes 3 = System Admin, agnostic to which model is primary\n- [x] Updated MEMORY.md with **Status Transparency Protocol**: emoji brief status (`🧠`, `🖋️`, `🛠️`) for long/multi-step tasks, delete/unsend tool logs within ~3s, keep emoji status during work then remove at end\n- [x] Updated Facefy Clean Output Protocol with Tool Log Cleanup + Transparent Cleanup rules\n- [x] Created and populated `Solar_Project/solar_bot_plan.md` (then moved to `.trash/Solar_Project_test_2026-05-08_0546` per user delete order)\n- [x] OpenClaw gateway restart — config validates OK, gateway health probe OK, services running\n\n### In Progress\n- (none currently)\n\n### Blocked\n- Auto-unsend/delete of Telegram messages is NOT natively supported by OpenClaw — requires bot-level code change (python-telegram-bot `deleteMessage` after ~3s delay). Rules in MEMORY.md acknowledge this limitation.\n- Memory search (`memory_search`) is temporarily unavailable — \"database is not open\" error. Falls back to SocratiCode search.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Local MCP install over global**: Installed MCP packages in `~/.openclaw/mcp-node` instead of global npm to avoid polluting Hermes's Node environment\n- **Hermes 3 only, keep nomic-embed-text**: User wanted only `hermes3:8b`; kept `nomic-embed-text` because SocratiCode uses it for embeddings\n- **Agnostic routing over fixed primary**: Changed from \"GPT-5.5 as mandatory boss\" to \"current model as Architect\" — any model can be primary, MiniMax/Hermes 3 always handle content/tech work respectively\n- **Silent tool usage by default**: Removed `[เรียกใช้เครื่องมือ: ...]` announcement pattern; emoji status only for multi-step tasks\n\n## Next Steps\n1. No immediate next steps — last user message was approving the Status Transparency Protocol update (completed)\n2. If user wants to test the emoji status system, use it naturally on the next task\n3. If user wants actual auto-delete in Telegram, they'd need to implement bot-level code change (Python telegram bot with deleteMessage after 3s delay)\n4. If Ollama MCP tools are needed for actual tasks, they are now configured and ready\n\n## Critical Context\n- OpenClaw config: `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` (backup at `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak`)\n- Ollama models: `hermes3:8b` (primary local), `qwen2.5:3b`, `moondream`, `nomic-embed-text`\n- Ollama MCP server path: `/home/apinan/.openclaw/mcp-node/node_modules/.bin/ollama-mcp-server`\n- Workspace path: `/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace`\n- Solar Project trash: `/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/.trash/Solar_Project_test_2026-05-08_0546`\n- Ollama version: 0.23.0\n- OpenClaw version: 2026.5.6 (c97b9f7)\n- Node/npm: v22.22.2 / 10.9.7\n- Current model routing: `thaigq/deepseek-v4-pro:cloud` (primary), `thaigq/deepseek-v4-flash:cloud`, `thaigq/minimax-m2.7:cloud`\n- Provider: `thaigq` at `https://ollama-pay.thaigqsoft.com/api/v1`\n\n<read-files>\n/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/skills/hermes-permission/SKILL.md\n/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/skills/socraticode-code/SKILL.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"9c969433","tokensBefore":185987,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/skills/hermes-permission/SKILL.md","/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/skills/socraticode-code/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"]},"fromHook":false}
